# Claude entry (product overlay)

This repository uses **agent-delivery-kit** for multi-agent delivery.

1. Read root `AGENTS.md` and `product.yaml`.
2. Follow `docs/code-quality-prerequisites.md` before coding.
3. Use delivery workflow only when the user asks for `交付` / status / gates.
4. Run `ruby scripts/doctor.rb` and `ruby scripts/validate_workflow.rb` when changing delivery state.

Short commands: see `COMMANDS.md`.
